{{Youmay|the matriarch of a rancor herd on Dathomir|Ketwol's starship, the ''[[Herd Mother]]''}}
A '''herd-mother''' (sometimes '''herd mother''' or '''herd leader''') was the matriarch of a [[Rancor/Legends|rancor]] herd on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]]. By the time of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], most rancor herds lived in symbiosis with the clans of [[Human/Legends|Human]] warrior women known as the [[Witches of Dathomir]].

One of the most remarkable sights on Dathomir came in the evening, when herd-mothers such as Tosh, whose herd was associated with the [[Singing Mountain Clan]], would sit their children down around a campfire in the starlight, and recount the oral history of their ancestors.

